Crocker'> <organization>University of California, Los Angeles (UCLA)</organization></author> <date year='1970' day='14' month='October' /> <abstract> <t>Taking advantage of the FJCC in Houston, I have scheduled a meeting of the Network Working Group in room Astro VII of the Astroworld Hotel at 8:00 p.m.  on Monday, November 16, 1970.</t></abstract></front>  <seriesInfo name='RFC' value='75' /> <format type='TXT' octets='1318' target='http://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc75.txt' /> </reference>
